Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 2025-12-31

This Privacy Policy explains how this Discord bot (“the Bot”) collects, uses, stores, and protects data. By using the Bot, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

The Bot collects only the minimum data required for functionality. This may include:

Discord User IDs

Discord Server (Guild) IDs

Channel IDs

Command usage and interaction metadata

Configuration data specific to a server

The Bot does not collect:

Message content (unless explicitly required for a feature)

Passwords, tokens, or authentication credentials

Personal information outside of what Discord provides via its API

2. How We Use Data

Collected data is used solely to:

Provide core Bot functionality

Store server or user preferences

Enable moderation or administrative features (if applicable)

Debug, maintain, and improve the Bot

Data is never used for advertising, tracking, or profiling.

3. Data Storage & Retention

Data is stored only as long as necessary for the Bot to function.

Temporary data may be cached and automatically cleared.

Server-specific data is removed when the Bot is removed from a server, where technically feasible.

4. Data Sharing

The Bot does not sell, rent, or share collected data with third parties.

Data is not disclosed except when required by law or legal process.

5. User Rights & Control

You may:

Request deletion of server-specific data by removing the Bot from your server

Contact the Bot owner to request clarification or data removal (where applicable)

Note: Discord itself controls and processes data independently under its own Privacy Policy.

6. Security

Reasonable measures are taken to protect stored data, including:

Limited data collection

Restricted access to systems

Secure handling of credentials and secrets

However, no system can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.

7. Compliance With Discord Policies

This Privacy Policy is designed to comply with:

Discord Terms of Service

Discord Developer Terms

Discord API and Data Handling Policies

8. Changes to This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated at any time. Continued use of the Bot after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.

9. Contact

If you have questions, concerns, or data requests, contact:

Discord: russianhelmet_

GitHub: Open an issue in this repository
